divs: Sighting Details I was sitting in class when I happened to look out the window, and I saw something hovering around the grain elevator! Now I am a streght A student, seeing something I can't identify realy alarms me! I have seen birds and helicopters flying around the elivator but this was nothing like it. What ever it was it hovered for about 1 minute, then started spiriling around as if to pick up speed. It then zoomed of and was lost in a bank of trees. I was scared, but managed to remain calm.
Summary: It flew around the grain elevator then took off at a VERY high rate of speed.
